HEADWORD: Melenite
<hw>Mel"e*nite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>me`li</grk> honey.]</ety> <def>An explosive of great destructive
power; -- so called from its color, which resembles honey.</def>⟦br⟧
